name: tezos-artcast giveaway - Surrounded
description: A giveaway made for the November 3rd 2021 edition of the Tezos ArtCast. The ventral and dorsal side of a cowboy may be surrounded by the body of a centipede. The sound of galloping hoofbeats may be heard if one chooses to hear it. An illustration by Little Old Man. This is an open edition to be burned back after the show.
